2.2 

Debian packaging added, changed to DeviceImpl, change launcher

----

Device Server for processing attributes (or generating new ones).
It is a "PySignalSimulator on Steroids", which incorporates:
-FFT calculation
-Gaussian peak fitting
-Signal Filtering (all functions from scipy.signal)
-general scipy functions
Comment on the version src-2.1 :

